Qatar raised salaries and pensions
for its citizens,  Qatar News Agency  reported, citing a decision
by the nationâ€™s ruler.  The basic salary and pensions of Qatari civilian employees
were increased 60 percent as of Sept. 1, the state-run  news
agency  said.  Military officers received a 120 percent raise and military
personnel of other ranks received a 50 percent increase, the
